items.title: 2 people found dead in JetBlue plane landing gear at Fort Lauderdale-Hollywood International Airport
items.description: The bodies were found during a routine inspection after the plane landed.

items.title: Indiana serial killer's victims could be identified amid new push
items.description: Investigators estimated at least 25 people were buried at Harold Baumeister's estate, based on evidence that included 10,000 bones and bone fragments.

items.title: 10 gunmen killed in shootout with police amid cartel turf battles
items.description: The early morning shootout happened during a joint patrol by police and the military in Guanajuato.

items.title: Controversial Trump picks like Sebastian Gorka likely to bypass Senate scrutiny
items.description: Sebastian Gorka failed security screenings during Trump's first term, but could return as White House counterterrorism chief.

items.title: Medical debt banned from credit reports by new Biden administration rule
items.description: Unpaid medical bills will no longer appear on credit reports under a final rule announced by the Biden administration.
